net.rim.device.api.collection.util
Class BasicFilteredListResult

java.lang.Object
  net.rim.device.api.collection.util.BasicFilteredListResult

public class BasicFilteredListResult
extends Object

A basic implementation of FilteredListResult, which only contains the _results object, for storing the matches obtained from BasicFilteredList.

Since:
BlackBerry API 5.0.0

_requestedFieldNames

public String[] _requestedFieldNames
The names of the data fields that were requested for display purposes (or any other purpose). These indicate what the requestedFields represent. These are in the same order as the _requestedFields array. This is null if not from a data source (i.e. from an array of strings or objects).

Since:
BlackBerry API 5.0.0

_requestedFieldValues

public String[][] _requestedFieldValues
The strings of the data fields that were requested for display purposes (or any other purpose). These are in the same order as the _requestedFields array. It is multidimensional because some fields can have more than one value, such as BasicFilteredList.DATA_FIELD_CONTACTS_EMAIL. This is null if not from a data source (i.e. from an array of strings or objects).

Since:
BlackBerry API 5.0.0
